The Obsidian Priest~
The Obsidian Priest stands here
~
It stands here, chanting in a voice impossibly low for any human to make.
The long dark robes that enshroud this figure seem to have a life of its
own, as they slowly glide through the air.  Trying to see below the large
hood of the creature before you, you see only darkness.  You feel that
something is not quite right, and then you realize there is no breeze-no
sound at all, only the relentless chanting.  The only thing that saves you
from panic is the soothing webs of healing magics that have been layered
upon you.  
~
