Obsidian Castle Entrance~
You are standing on the black drawbridge to the Obsidian Castle.  As you
look more closely to the walls, you notice that they are indeed polished
multi-ton blocks of pure obsidian.  Tall spires stretch up towards the
clouds several hundred feet.  Squinting, you noticed the person who was just
watching you has left the window in one of the spires.  The doorway into the
Obsidian Castle is a massive stone head of a dragon, its maw gaped open. 
The fangs of the head are almost as tall as you are, and some even have dark
red stains.  
~
