Meeting Chambers~
A table of red and yellow tiger, faceted with opal, rests in the middle
of the room.  Enough seats for the entire staff of the kingdom have been
placed around the table, and seem to have been in constant use.  Maps of all
sorts lay upon the smooth surface of the table, markers of armies and cities
in various places.  You turn around to leave and stop suddenly.  Two twelve
foot statues of knights in shining armor lean against the walls to the right
and left of the entrance.  Somehow, you feel the sensation that they are
watching you...  
