#46103
Teleportation Chambers~
The room is lit only by a single torch on the wall to your right.  The
darkness is so thick in this room that even your spells cannot pierce it. 
Before you turn to leave, a whisper echoes off the walls.  "Tell me where
you wish to go, traveler."  You begin to wonder where he will allow you to
go, when you feel the hairs on the back of your neck stiffen.  The torch
flickers for a moment, then a brilliant red flame explodes on the opposite
wall.  Before your eyes have time to blink-the flame dies down and you are
able to read the glowing letters.  "This is the sign."  Said the whisper
again.  
~
